snippet.title: Medieval Dynasty | Crossplay Update Release | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Crossplay Update is now available on all platforms! Get it today and build the greatest Medieval Dynasty, together!
Steam 👉 https://bit.ly/MedievalDynasty_Steam
EpicGames 👉 https://store.epicgames.com/pl/p/medieval-dynasty
Microsoft Store 👉 https://www.xbox.com/pl-PL/games/store/medieval-dynasty/9PDDP6ML6XHF
PlayStation Store 👉 https://store.playstation.com/pl-pl/product/EP3550-CUSA34020_00-MEDIEVALDYNPS4EU
Xbox 👉 https://www.xbox.com/pl-PL/games/store/medieval-dynasty/9PDDP6ML6XHF
GOG.com 👉 https://www.gog.com/pl/game/medieval_dynasty

The day has come and all players can now enjoy the new features, together! For the exact list of changes including added content, fixes and updates read our newest Steam post 👉  https://bit.ly/CrossplayUpdate_Changelog
